  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2021-04-15",
    "date": "2021-05-14T22:58:30Z",
    "text": "Ending China's Exit Ban for American Citizens Act of 2021 \n\nThis bill bars an official of China's government from obtaining a visa to enter the United States if the official was involved in prohibiting a U.S. citizen from leaving China in an attempt to achieve certain goals, such as convincing a relative of the U.S. citizen to submit to Chinese government custody for prosecution. Any existing visa belonging to such an official shall be revoked."
